#. type: Plain text
#: emacs-lisp-intro.texi:19482
msgid ""
"Interestingly, GNU Emacs possesses a file called @file{ring.el} that "
"provides many of the features we just discussed.  But functions such as "
"@code{kill-ring-yank-pointer} do not use this library, possibly because they "
