#. type: group
#: emacs-lisp-intro.texi:21344
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"(defun lengths-list-many-files (list-of-files)\n"
"  \"Return list of lengths of defuns in LIST-OF-FILES.\"\n"
"  (let (lengths-list)\n"
